Nvm had to open the full message. I've already been submitted at most of those.

I think they are just interviewing so they can justify to some hypothetical lawyer that they need to hire H1B visas because no one here is "qualified". Which is because no American wants to work on their stupid project without asking questions as to why are we doing this? You don't get that kind of honest expression from people starving for money.
